PWA / iOS splash screens shown during app launch.

iOS splash size matrix (portrait):
  qcap-splash-1290x2796.png    iPhone 15 Pro Max
  qcap-splash-1179x2556.png    iPhone 15 / 15 Pro
  qcap-splash-1170x2532.png    iPhone 12/13/14 (Pro)
  qcap-splash-1080x2340.png    Android (density-adaptive)
  qcap-splash-2048x2732.png    iPad Pro 12.9"
  qcap-splash-1668x2388.png    iPad Pro 11"

Design rules:
  - Background: brand-dark #0f172a
  - Centred mark at ~30 % of the shortest edge
  - Do not include text (renders differently across devices)

Android reads splash from `manifest.webmanifest → background_color`
and `theme_color` — no per-device assets required.
